name: The Arrowhead Barrette - Salmon
description:
We are SO excited to be introducing hair barrettes into the Hanging Vultures accessory line. 

This style features a gorgeous peach bead and beautiful cream leather, it is fascinated by a classic butterfly barrette. Looks great with a crop top and sandals. 

Width: 4 inches
Height: 2 1/2 inches

name: Rockin' Red Tribal Earrings
description:
All earrings are handmade one of a kind pieces and will not be duplicated.

Not for the faint of heart, these showstoppers are made of 100% genuine leather and hand sewn glass bead-work. Wear one or wear both, these gems are surprisingly light weight and full of fun movement.  Looks awesome with a maxi skirt and a casual tank!
